    "v3": "But the pain which He endured, Alleluia! Our salvation hath procured, Alleluia! Now above the sky He&#39;s king, Alleluia! Where the angels ever sing, Alleluia!",
    "v4": "Sing we to our God above, Alleluia! Praise eternal as His love, Alleluia! Praise Him, all you heav&#39;nly host, Alleluia! Father, Son, and Holy Ghost, Alleluia!"
  },
